Dude... It's a humor line. New Galio is an idiot. That's the joke. He obviously kicked the crap out of a house and thought it was cool, and doesn't get that it wasn't fighting because he, too, is a piece of architecture.

Just look at his derpy face, now re-listen to the line while looking at it: {{champion:3}}

HE WANTS TO FIGHT THE SUN.
